{"article_id":"NF4ZH4OrQVBHYAHv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Trump administration declared Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that it 's up to North Korea to follow through on its threats","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to cancel a summit with Kim Jong Un ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the United States remains prepared to meet .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"`` We 'll see what happens , ''","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Trump told reporters during a photo opportunity with the president of Uzbekistan ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"adding","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that he will insist on North Korean `` denuclearization '' as a condition of talks .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Earlier , White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders said of the North Koreans :","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"`` If they want to meet","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"we ' ll be ready","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and if they don ' t ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that ' s OK too . ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Suggesting","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that the threats by Kim 's government may be pre-summit posturing ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Sanders also said ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"`` this is something","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that we fully expected , ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and that the administration remains `` hopeful ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"the June 12 meeting will happen .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Trump and Sanders both said","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"the administration has not received formal notification from the North Koreans about potential problems with the summit .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Hours after protesting U.S.-South Korea joint military exercises ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"the North Koreans issued a second threat","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to cancel the Trump-Kim meeting","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"by rejecting the idea","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that they would unilaterally give up nuclear weapons ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"their country would end up like Libya or Iraq .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` If the U.S. is trying to drive us into a corner","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"to force our unilateral nuclear abandonment ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"we will no longer be interested in such dialogue","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"and can not but reconsider our proceeding to the DPRK-U.S. summit , ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"said the translated statement","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"attributed to Kim Kye Gwan , North Korea 's first vice-minister of Foreign Affairs .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Trump announced last week","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"he would meet with Kim June 12 in Singapore","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"to discuss an agreement on nuclear weapons .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"For months , the American president has urged China and other countries to cut off economic aid to North Korea","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"until Kim gives up his weapons programs .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"In its latest statement , the North Koreans suggested","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"they would not give up nukes","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"even in exchange for economic assistance from the U.S. and allies .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The statement attacked Trump aides ,","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"singling out National Security Adviser John Bolton in particular ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"for promoting what the North Koreans called `` the assertions of so-called Libya mode of nuclear abandonment . ''","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"Libyan leader Muammar Gadhafi gave up programs for weapons of mass destruction in 2003 .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"He was deposed and killed in 2011","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"after a rebellion","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"sparked by the Arab Spring .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"The U.S.-led invasion of Iraq in 2003 ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"based on faulty intelligence about weapons of mass destruction ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"toppled Saddam Hussein 's government .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"North Korea threatens to cancel Donald Trump-Kim Jong Un meeting","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"North Korea warns","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"it may cancel summit with Trump","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"if it has to give up nukes","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Bolton , a longtime critic of the North Korean regime , has cited the `` Libya model '' as a potential process","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"by which Kim could dismantle its nuclear programs .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Sanders , however , said","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that is not administration policy :","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"`` This is the President Trump model .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"He 's going to run this the way","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"he sees fit . ''","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"In an earlier statement , North Korea criticized ongoing joint military exercises by the United States and South Korea ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"that was a reason","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"to rethink the Trump-Kim summit .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"U.S. officials ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"caught by surprise ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"they have received no formal notification from the North or South Korean governments ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and no formal protest of the military exercises from Kim 's government .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"The U.S. Defense Department said","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"the military exercises are annual events ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"designed to help the U.S.-South Korea alliance defend itself in case of attack .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"`` While we will not discuss specifics ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"the defensive nature of these combined exercises has been clear for many decades","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and has not changed , ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"said Army Col. Robert Manning , a Pentagon spokesman .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"It 's hard to know how seriously to treat Kim 's threats about the Trump meeting ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"analysts said .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"They could be Kim 's way","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"of pushing back at perceptions","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that Trump is seeking more from North Korea","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"than he is willing to give .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"The two sides have described denuclearization quite differently ;","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"while Trump wants North Korea to fully disarm its nukes ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"the North Koreans have in the past called on the United States to pull back its nuclear defense umbrella across the Korean Peninsula .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Kim could also be working with Chinese President Xi Jinping ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"who wants to show","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"that he will be a player in the fate of his nuclear-armed neighbor ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"some analysts speculated .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"anybody knows , ''","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"said Aaron David Miller , a former State Department negotiator for presidents from both political parties .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"`` There 's a high degree of opacity here . '' Kim may be starting to look at what kinds of concessions he can extract from Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"said Tom Nichols , professor of National Security Affairs at the Naval War College .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"Calling it `` a classic ploy , ''","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"Nichols said","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"that `` the North Koreans waited","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"until a time and a place was set ,","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"and for the president to fully commit himself ,","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"before they reversed course","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"and withdrew their original offers .","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"Now they 're seeing just how badly the Americans want this meeting . ''","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Sen. John Kennedy , R-La. ,","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"speaking on Fox Business Network ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"described Kim as a `` goon '' and a `` butcher , ''","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"but said","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"the North Korean leader needs some kind of deal","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"because sanctions are starving his people .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Kennedy described Kim 's threats as part of the negotiating process ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"and added ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"China completely controls Kim Jong Un . ''","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Trump has vowed to keep economic pressure on North Korea throughout the negotiating process .","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"The North Koreans went ahead","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"and canceled planned meetings Wednesday with South Korean counterparts .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"The two sides had planned to discuss new efforts","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"to reduce border tensions ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"including proposals","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"to reunite families","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"separated during the Korean War of the early 1950s .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"The South and North Koreans have also talked about a formal peace treaty ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"as they are technically still at war ;","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"the original Korean conflict ended with an armistice","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"signed in 1953 .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"In announcing the cancellation of the meeting with the South Koreans ,","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"the North Koreans said","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that `` the United States will also have to undertake careful deliberations about the fate of the planned North Korea-U.S. summit in light of this provocative military ruckus","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"jointly conducted with the South Korean authorities . ''","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Trump supporters have said","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"he should be considered for the Nobel Peace Prize for his efforts","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"to bring North Korea to the table .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"In its latest threat","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"to cancel the Trump-Kim summit ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"the North Koreans took aim at Trump 's reputation","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"and alluded to his criticism of previous presidents over their handling of Korean issues .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"`` If President Trump follows in the footsteps of his predecessors ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"he will be recorded as more tragic and unsuccessful president than his predecessors , far from his initial ambition","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"to make unprecedented success , ''","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"said the translated statement .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"`` If they want to meet , ''","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"she said ,","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"`` the president will certainly be ready . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":299,"left":0,"right":298,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":298,"left":203,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":158,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":152,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":1,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nucle